modules.description: Processes Mustache templates by reading files and injecting structured data. Works with `Yocaml.Path.t` paths and data types implementing `Yocaml.Required.DATA_INJECTABLE`. Used to generate text output like HTML or config files from templates and OCaml values.

Processes Mustache templates by reading files and injecting structured data. Works with `Yocaml.Path.t` paths and data types implementing `Yocaml.Required.DATA_INJECTABLE`. Used to generate text output like HTML or config files from templates and OCaml values. Transforms normalized data into injectable format and renders templates with optional strict mode for missing keys.
